$ Excel helpers: insert a comment

The following macro inserts a → Microsoft/Office/Excel/Object-Model/Comment[comment] in the currently selected cell and opens it so that the usual right mouse click after inserting a comment is
not necessary.

gh|about-Excel|/helpers/insertComment.bas||

sa:

  → Microsoft/Office/Excel/Object-Model/Comment#excel-comment-show-hide[Show/hide comments with a mouse click]

  → Microsoft/Office/Excel/helpers
